This little plasmoid provides a configuration interface and a switch to start/stop Redshift daemon. See Redshift websites for more detailed info <http://jonls.dk/redshift/>.

Developed by:
Diego Cristina <diegocc100 AT gmail DOT com>
Simone Gaiarin <simgunz AT gmail DOT com>

Code under GPLv3 license (see COPYING)

Requires:
KDE SC 4.x
Redshift 

How to install:
plasmapkg -i redshift.plasmoid
